  "title": "Customer Service Officer (Full Time / Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Summary:</strong></u></p>\n<p>The Customer Service Officer plays a vital role in supporting the School Head in the daily operations of the school. This multifaceted role encompasses a wide range of responsibilities, including enrollment activities, class management, record-keeping, school maintenance, prospecting, and cashier duties.</p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p>\n<p><strong>Financial &amp; Enrollment:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Market and promote CLC courses to potential students.</li>\n  <li>Engage in daily prospecting activities.</li>\n  <li>Assist in the preparation of enrollment reports.</li>\n  <li>Perform cashier duties, including the collection and banking of daily cash and cheques.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and follow up on outstanding payments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Area Marketing:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Collaborate with the Centre Manager to conduct Area Marketing and Industry Colleagues' Surveys.</li>\n  <li>Distribute leaflets, brochures, course information, and promotional materials.</li>\n  <li>Assist in designing and producing in-house promotional materials.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Customer Service:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage the customer service counter, ensuring a high level of service quality.</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service by addressing customer and prospect inquiries, feedback, and complaints.</li>\n  <li>Attend to all requests from teachers, students, and customers.</li>\n  <li>Conduct Customer Satisfaction Surveys.</li>\n  <li>Maintain up-to-date files and records.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>General School Operations:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct daily checks to ensure school safety and cleanliness.</li>\n  <li>Monitor the condition of studios and equipment on a daily basis.</li>\n  <li>Update and maintain notice boards.</li>\n  <li>Handle sales of stocks and textbooks to students, teachers, and customers.</li>\n  <li>Monitor stock levels.</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing operations reports.</li>\n  <li>Update the SMS system.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Other Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle daily general administration tasks and support service operations.</li>\n  <li>Assist in organizing and participating in school activities.</li>\n  <li>Address any other related issues as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably, candidates should have sales experience.</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office.</li>\n  <li>A team player with a positive attitude.</li>\n  <li>Part-time candidates are welcome to apply.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are a proactive and service-oriented individual with the necessary qualifications and skills, we encourage you to apply for this role.</p>\n<p>Join our team and contribute to our school's success !</p>",
